1
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:10,560
♪Trapped in this tiny world♪

2
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:14,440
♪I'm crushed into dust♪

3
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:19,000
♪I meddle around without any mercy♪

4
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:22,160
♪I'm my own pawn♪

5
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:26,360
♪I sigh at my fate♪

6
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:31,360
♪Numerous people are under my control♪

7
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:37,880
♪All the sand is washed away♪

8
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:43,880
♪An old dream fades♪

9
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:50,560
♪A bumpy path lies ahead♪

10
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:54,880
♪Traps within traps, I never make mistakes♪

11
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:58,000
♪I take a risk at every step♪

12
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:03,400
♪Even in disputes, I break through with my life♪

13
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:06,280
♪Schemes within schemes, I prison myself♪

14
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:09,600
♪Each link swaps bluff and truth♪

15
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:12,480
♪The world is my Weiqi game board♪

16
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:18,120
♪Everything's just fleeting♪

17
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:24,320
♪The play begins♪

18
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,520
♪No return is expected♪

19
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:33,880
♪The flame is gone, whether we win or lose♪

20
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:36,360
♪The wind never ceases. I hold the reins♪

21
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,510
[Ashes To Crown]

22
00:01:37,510 --> 00:01:41,680
[Adapted from Xixing's novel, Empress of the State of Chu]

23
00:01:42,470 --> 00:01:45,000
[Episode 23]

24
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,900
A group of Northern Desert killers

25
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:18,820
ambushed Jiu.

26
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,920
They chased Jiu for dozens of li

27
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,140
until he was cornered on a cliff

28
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:25,240
with no way out.

29
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:28,000
I heard he was seriously injured.

30
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:32,240
I guess he jumped off the cliff for the sake of dignity.

31
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,120
I swear on General Chu's armor.

32
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,920
I will stay alive

33
00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,640
and return the armor.

34
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,320
Both.

35
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,200
The armor and me.

36
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,840
I give you my word.

37
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:10,980
I will come back alive.

38
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,000
Jiu,

39
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,360
you liar.

40
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,760
Why did you break your promise?

41
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:49,960
Your Highness!

42
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,520
Your Highness!

43
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:52,840
Your Highness,

44
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,120
we received anonymous news.

45
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,280
Those killers aren't from

46
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,080
the Northern Desert

47
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,080
but Xiaonan Prefecture.

48
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,360
Xiao Xun declared himself king

49
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,800
and feared Yunzhong.

50
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,760
So, he wanted the Northern Desert King

51
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,400
to be a hostage.

52
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,120
Anyone who destabilizes my state

53
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,400
will be killed.

54
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:23,840
Issue my order.

55
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,800
All troops in Yunzhong stand ready for war.

56
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,760
I'll make Xiao Xun

57
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,860
pay blood for blood.

58
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,880
Great, no corpses were found.

59
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,800
The Northern Desert King died within this state.

60
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:53,280
Chu Zhao lost her sharpest blade too.

61
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,040
Tie Ying,

62
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:57,280
what expression

63
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,280
do you think she has now?

64
00:04:58,880 --> 00:04:59,760
Xie Yanlai is dead.

65
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,680
The frontier troops will be demoralized.

66
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:03,040
Your Majesty,

67
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,500
a wise plan.

68
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,640
Wise?

69
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,760
That wasn't my plan.

70
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,080
I have to say

71
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,320
Xie Yanfang's trick

72
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:19,460
to find a scapegoat

73
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,440
was really brilliant.

74
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,200
Are you saying...?

75
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:25,700
He knew Chu Zhao would go mad.

76
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,980
He knew she would

77
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:30,000
blame me for everything.

78
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:31,580
However, Chu Zhao

79
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,740
focuses on fighting desperately

80
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,280
against me.

81
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:40,160
So, she might never realize

82
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:42,100
that she's being used.

83
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,400
Your Majesty.

84
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:44,560
Your Majesty.

85
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:46,840
Your Majesty,

86
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:47,940
urgent report.

87
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,480
Her Highness led frontier troops

88
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,720
and broke through Qingyu Pass.

89
00:05:50,940 --> 00:05:52,220
They're heading for Xiaonan.

90
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:55,860
At last, she's coming.

91
00:05:58,540 --> 00:06:02,170
[Xiaonan]

92
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:10,800
Zhao,

93
00:06:12,140 --> 00:06:13,820
why bother to make such a fuss?

94
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,320
You took your elite troops

95
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,720
to my prefecture.

96
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,400
Have you come to seek refuge with me?

97
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,760
Xiao Xun,

98
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,320
you rebelled,

99
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,560
murdered my general,

100
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,040
killed the enemy king,

101
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,360
and broke the alliance.

102
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,840
Today,

103
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:32,360
as the Grand Princess of State,

104
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,000
I'll punish the traitors!

105
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,440
I have the late Emperor's edict.

106
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,600
I'm the legitimate heir to the throne,

107
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,560
favored by heaven.

108
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,520
The real traitor

109
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,000
remains to be seen.

110
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,280
Faking an imperial edict

111
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:47,920
is an even greater offense.

112
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,800
Murdered your general?

113
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,040
Killed the enemy king?

114
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,360
You don't think

115
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,640
I killed Xie Yanlai, do you?

116
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:00,000
You always have an excuse to condemn me.

117
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,080
Chu Zhao,

118
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,400
for your personal revenge,

119
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,440
you're starting a war.

120
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,320
You killed a general

121
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,520
and brought chaos on the frontier.

122
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,080
How dare you say this is just an excuse?

123
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,000
Soldiers,

124
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,440
kill the traitors!

125
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:17,880
Kill!

126
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,560
Kill!

127
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:23,240
- Kill! - Kill!

128
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,920
Kill!

129
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,340
Kill!

130
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:30,160
Kill!

131
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:38,020
Kill!

132
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,520
Kill!

133
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,840
Xiao Xun has been captured.

134
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,120
You should all surrender!

135
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,240
Deng Yi,

136
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:10,960
how dare you...

137
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,960
I didn't expect that.

138
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,960
Deng Yi helped me win.

139
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,640
He also made me lose.

140
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:37,540
I'm the one who defeated you.

141
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,480
From now on,

142
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,640
you'll be the dowager.

143
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,560
Just enjoy a great life.

144
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,680
Oh, my silly son.

145
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,080
A mother

146
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,120
cares nothing for a great life.

147
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:57,080
All I want is that you can

148
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,400
stay safe.

149
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,720
This is the talisman I got for you.

150
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,000
You will stay healthy

151
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,400
and watch me

152
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,760
rise to a position

153
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,480
second only to the Emperor.

154
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,720
Chu Zhao had the talisman

155
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,720
sent to me.

156
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,060
She's threatening me.

157
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,840
Then what will you do, My Lord?

158
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,360
What can I do?

159
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,400
With this talisman,

160
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:21,920
she's warning me

161
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,040
that my mother is alive

162
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,400
and she has her.

163
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,120
Zhao,

164
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,880
I have true feelings for you.

165
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,400
I never meant to hurt you.

166
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:45,720
Is that so?

167
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,000
Then in my past life,

168
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:52,220
who strangled me

169
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:56,020
with white silk?

170
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,420
Your... Your past life?

171
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:09,320
Yes.

172
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,760
I lived once before.

173
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:16,620
I died too.

174
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:21,340
You killed me.

175
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,160
Why?

176
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:26,660
Why did you do this to my clan?

177
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,780
Why did you do this to me?

178
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:30,060
Why?

179
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:41,140
Are you scared?

180
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:45,380
In my past life,

181
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,740
when you massacred my clan

182
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,600
and cut off my father's head,

183
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:52,580
you weren't this cowardly.

184
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,120
What past life?

185
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:56,820
This is ridiculous.

186
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,160
How could anyone be reborn?

187
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:00,660
Zhao,

188
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:02,860
that must be a dream.

189
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:04,400
You can't hate me

190
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,680
for an illusory dream.

191
00:11:06,140 --> 00:11:06,640
Zhao.

192
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,400
It wasn't a dream.

193
00:11:08,980 --> 00:11:10,220
It was a purgatory

194
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:11,460
I truly experienced.

195
00:11:13,020 --> 00:11:14,480
Illusory?

196
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:19,080
My pain was real.

197
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:22,240
My father's blood was real.

198
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:24,240
Zhao.

199
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:26,000
It was true

200
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:28,180
that all my clansmen suffered!

201
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:30,900
Zhao.

202
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:45,900
You never meant to hurt me?

203
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,440
You hated me badly

204
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,000
and wanted my father dead.

205
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:55,740
No.

206
00:11:55,980 --> 00:11:57,460
You wanted my clan dead.

207
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:11,300
You only love the throne,

208
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:12,860
power,

209
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:15,140
and yourself.

210
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,740
Go to the underground

211
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:20,580
with your hypocrisy.

212
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:36,400
Xiao Xun,

213
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:38,520
for all the civilians

214
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,440
who suffered because of you...

215
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,360
For my father.

216
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,080
For Jiu.

217
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,960
And for me.

218
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,520
Xiao Xun,

219
00:12:57,660 --> 00:12:59,160
you must die.

220
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,280
Xie Yanlai

221
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,200
wasn't killed...

222
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,520
In the third year of Xingping,

223
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:16,800
Xiao Xun, the Prince of Xiaonan,

224
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:20,080
got General Xie Yanlai killed.

225
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:21,600
He colluded with enemies,

226
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,440
trying to ruin the State of Chu!

227
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,280
As the Grand Princess,

228
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:30,800
I'm executing him to serve justice!

229
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,800
♪Trapped in this tiny world♪

230
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,960
♪I'm crushed into dust♪

231
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:42,440
♪I meddle around without any mercy♪

232
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:46,480
♪I'm my own pawn♪

233
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:49,800
♪I sigh at my fate♪

234
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:55,800
♪Numerous people are under my control♪

235
00:13:58,280 --> 00:14:01,640
♪All the sand is washed away♪

236
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:08,160
♪An old dream fades♪

237
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:15,520
♪A bumpy path lies ahead♪

238
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:18,760
♪Traps within traps, I never make mistakes♪

239
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:22,020
♪I take a risk at every step♪

240
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:27,180
♪Even in disputes, I break through with my life♪

241
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:30,420
♪Schemes within schemes, I prison myself♪

242
00:14:30,460 --> 00:14:33,140
♪Each link swaps bluff and truth♪

243
00:14:33,620 --> 00:14:36,620
♪The world is my Weiqi game board♪

244
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:42,480
♪Everything's just fleeting♪

245
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,360
You picked the wrong side.

246
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,360
A loser like me

247
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,160
won't argue.

248
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,920
You may die with ease.

249
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,280
Your mother is innocent.

250
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,240
I'll take care of her.

251
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,240
Your Highness, I beg you

252
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,800
not to tell her what becomes of me.

253
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:09,600
♪I follow my destined path♪

254
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:11,360
All right.

255
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:15,180
♪All the sand is washed away♪

256
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:21,040
♪An old dream fades♪

257
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:24,960
♪A bumpy path lies ahead♪

258
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,160
Your Highness,

259
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:30,400
thank you!

260
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:34,440
♪I take a risk at every step♪

261
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:37,240
♪The world is my Weiqi game board♪

262
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:37,760
The Xiao Clan

263
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,880
will be reduced to commoners

264
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,520
and exiled to the frontier.

265
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:51,040
♪The play begins♪

266
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:54,240
♪No return is expected♪

267
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:56,300
♪The flame is gone♪

268
00:15:56,300 --> 00:15:58,820
♪Whether we win or lose♪

269
00:15:58,820 --> 00:16:02,470
[Xiaonan]

270
00:16:03,260 --> 00:16:08,240
♪I hold the reins♪

271
00:16:23,020 --> 00:16:25,180
Xie Yanlai

272
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:27,160
wasn't killed...

273
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,080
Your Highness.

274
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:34,880
Your Highness,

275
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:36,520
what's wrong?

276
00:16:37,260 --> 00:16:38,500
Before Xiao Xun died,

277
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,720
he said he didn't kill Jiu.

278
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:44,460
Le,

279
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:47,000
is it possible that...?

280
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:48,400
That traitor was still deceitful

281
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:49,160
even before dying.

282
00:16:49,500 --> 00:16:50,780
How could you believe him?

283
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,480
But I feel something is not right.

284
00:16:58,520 --> 00:16:59,200
Your Highness,

285
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:00,760
you're overthinking.

286
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:02,620
Shall we rest early tonight?

287
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:03,620
Let me help you.

288
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:08,400
Your Highness,

289
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:09,680
Mr. Zhu is out there

290
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:10,620
with a report to make.

291
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,120
Show him in.

292
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:20,760
Greetings.

293
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:23,640
You asked me to investigate

294
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:24,760
the Wangcheng case.

295
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:25,920
We found

296
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,120
a suspicious merchant

297
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,360
named Yu Shang.

298
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,480
Go on.

299
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,120
He runs a small business

300
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,240
with little contact with big merchants.

301
00:17:33,520 --> 00:17:34,640
But he's very friendly.

302
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,560
Many people in town

303
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,680
remember him.

304
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,200
When Yu Shang left the Capital,

305
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:44,740
he was holding a bottle of wine,

306
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:46,960
known as "Immortal Wine".

307
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:49,340
During those days, we searched

308
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:50,640
all the taverns and teahouses.

309
00:17:50,980 --> 00:17:52,180
We even checked the banquets

310
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:53,100
of big clans.

311
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:54,840
It seemed an impossible job.

312
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,480
But we succeeded.

313
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,440
Those days, Yu Shang

314
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,840
went to some taverns.

315
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:01,060
In one of the taverns,

316
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,260
Liang Qiang was there.

317
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:03,560
More importantly,

318
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,560
a waiter witnessed

319
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,080
Yu Shang meeting Xie Yanfang

320
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:07,960
in a private room

321
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:10,020
on the second floor of Lianchi House.

322
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:13,940
Xie Yanfang?

323
00:18:14,740 --> 00:18:15,860
Maybe that was a coincidence.

324
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:18,140
We're also carefully investigating

325
00:18:18,380 --> 00:18:19,620
other guests who were there.

326
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:21,280
But too much time has passed.

327
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:22,940
We can't recover all details.

328
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,240
Not a coincidence.

329
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:31,040
He was involved with two key figures,

330
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:32,680
Yu Shang and Liang Qiang.

331
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,480
It couldn't be a coincidence.

332
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:38,280
I'm afraid everything was...

333
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:46,620
That was

334
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,640
a really marvelous plan.

335
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,560
Xiao Xun and Deng Yi are dead.

336
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:50,980
So is Xie Yanlai.

337
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:53,440
Now, the Grand Princess stands alone.

338
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:54,560
No threat.

339
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,720
You only need to seize her command

340
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:57,760
of the frontier troops.

341
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,520
And His Majesty trusts you.

342
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:01,580
Your position is secure,

343
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:04,020
as the ruler of the world.

344
00:19:04,860 --> 00:19:05,820
For me,

345
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:08,180
controlling the game is what matters

346
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:11,660
more than being the ruler of the world.

347
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,480
Only those

348
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,720
blinded by hatred

349
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:18,500
would fail to see

350
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:20,340
such an obvious flaw.

351
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:21,760
I wonder

352
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:22,920
when the Grand Princess

353
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:24,200
will find out

354
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,800
that I am behind

355
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:29,280
all of this.

356
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:32,280
But by then,

357
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,520
she will have no choice

358
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:40,000
but to return to me.

359
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:46,200
General Liang,

360
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:49,080
how does it feel to be a prisoner

361
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:50,120
again?

362
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:54,660
What are you trying to say?

363
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:57,760
Just say it.

364
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,200
The day you got your title,

365
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,200
did you see Xie Yanfang?

366
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:07,740
I knew it.

367
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:09,980
At that banquet,

368
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:12,040
he toasted me from afar.

369
00:20:13,100 --> 00:20:13,900
Only then did I know

370
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:18,200
he was the one who had been helping me

371
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,880
in the past few years.

372
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:23,400
I didn't know that before.

373
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:23,840
Didn't?

374
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:24,160
I...

375
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,000
At Xinggu Pass,

376
00:20:26,220 --> 00:20:27,580
you let the enemy troops in

377
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,020
so that Wangcheng was lost

378
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,640
and your comrades died.

379
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:31,880
You didn't know?

380
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:34,660
You could have rejected the toast,

381
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,080
exposed his scheme,

382
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:38,240
or even have died in the battle

383
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:39,040
to prove loyalty.

384
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,520
But you chose

385
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:42,600
the dirtiest way.

386
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:44,900
I just wanted to make a name for myself.

387
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,020
The Xie Clan held great power.

388
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,500
If I rejected him...

389
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,940
You had countless chances

390
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,720
to turn back.

391
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,140
But after all,

392
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:57,820
you betrayed those

393
00:20:57,820 --> 00:20:58,860
who trusted you.

394
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:07,080
Today,

395
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,960
I'll question you for the soldiers

396
00:21:11,020 --> 00:21:11,660
who died unjustly.

397
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,760
How does it feel

398
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:16,940
to be promoted?

399
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,060
Soldiers in Wangcheng

400
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:34,380
never knew

401
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:39,100
their comrade had betrayed them

402
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:39,900
even before death.

403
00:22:07,180 --> 00:22:07,820
I...

404
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:14,320
I've learned my lesson.

405
00:22:26,020 --> 00:22:27,460
Liang Qiang killed himself last night.

406
00:22:28,580 --> 00:22:29,540
He got what he deserved.

407
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:35,760
Jiu,

408
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:38,640
wait and see.

409
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,040
I will make him

410
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:44,280
pay for everything he has done.

411
00:22:49,360 --> 00:22:50,440
Xie Yanfang always

412
00:22:50,980 --> 00:22:52,000
has a backup plan.

413
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:54,300
The autumn hunt is coming.

414
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:56,440
He will bring this up

415
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:57,740
in the court.

416
00:22:58,680 --> 00:22:59,600
On the day of the hunt,

417
00:23:00,580 --> 00:23:02,020
he will make his move.

418
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:03,060
Then we should

419
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,260
make early preparations.

420
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:05,840
Your Highness...

421
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:07,600
Have the Longwei Army

422
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:08,800
ambush in the hunting ground.

423
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:11,800
This time,

424
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:15,040
I'll show him

425
00:23:15,220 --> 00:23:16,620
how his trap

426
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:19,740
will be crushed.

427
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:26,720
Mr. Deng has just died.

428
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,000
His Majesty is young.

429
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:30,940
We need to make up for the Regent's absence.

430
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:32,260
I believe

431
00:23:33,140 --> 00:23:35,140
Mr. Xie is the best choice.

432
00:23:36,100 --> 00:23:38,800
- I second that. - I second that.

433
00:23:39,340 --> 00:23:40,420
- I second that. - I second that.

434
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:47,020
Mr. Xie is virtuous and talented.

435
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,320
He's worthy of this.

436
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:54,340
Your Highness works hard to command

437
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:55,240
the frontier troops.

438
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:57,240
I'll work together with you

439
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,160
to assist His Majesty.

440
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:02,040
The autumn hunt is coming.

441
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:03,960
Why don't we pray

442
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,880
for His Majesty during the hunt?

443
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,400
To hunt in this season,

444
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:09,320
I'm afraid...

445
00:24:09,320 --> 00:24:10,440
When the late Emperor lived,

446
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:12,040
he loved the autumn hunt

447
00:24:12,840 --> 00:24:14,720
to demonstrate our military might.

448
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,200
What do you think, Your Highness?

449
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:20,280
Mr. Xie,

450
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,200
it's a good idea.

451
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,320
Yu, don't be scared.

452
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:39,240
When you're around,

453
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,400
I won't be scared.

454
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,080
Even if I'm away

455
00:24:42,320 --> 00:24:43,440
and you're all alone,

456
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:44,840
don't be scared.

457
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:47,020
Because you've grown up.

458
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,320
You can protect yourself

459
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:50,080
and you're the Emperor

460
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:50,920
who protects his people.

461
00:24:51,980 --> 00:24:52,580
Come on, Yu.

462
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:54,620
Show me how well you can hunt.

463
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:18,000
Yu rides very well.

464
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:21,920
But he isn't good at archery.

465
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:23,720
An emperor doesn't need all skills.

466
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:25,360
He just needs to keep fit.

467
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:27,440
It's said you excel

468
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:28,560
in riding and archery.

469
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,120
Why don't you be his model?

470
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:31,560
Since Yu was little,

471
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:32,960
he has admired you.

472
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,760
All I seek in my life

473
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,760
is to help him become

474
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:37,760
an unparalleled emperor.

475
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,680
Whether I can be his model

476
00:25:42,280 --> 00:25:43,440
and whether my clan

477
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:44,680
can remain unmatched...

478
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:46,880
Neither of those matters.

479
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:49,800
I know

480
00:25:50,140 --> 00:25:51,100
you care for Yu

481
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:53,080
as well as our state.

482
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:55,280
For the court's long-term interests,

483
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:56,640
I want to issue a ban.

484
00:25:56,880 --> 00:25:58,040
Ban imperial in-laws from official posts.

485
00:25:59,140 --> 00:26:00,060
Mr. Xie,

486
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:01,340
what do you think?

487
00:26:02,040 --> 00:26:02,560
Very good.

488
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:05,360
Don't you think this is hegemony?

489
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:06,800
In my heart,

490
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:08,400
you will help Yu

491
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:10,640
dominate the entire world.

492
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:12,040
But I don't think

493
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:13,040
this is hegemony.

494
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,000
It's what you should do

495
00:26:15,040 --> 00:26:16,360
and what you have to do.

496
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,440
I pledge my life

497
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:21,080
to help you achieve this goal.

498
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:22,880
It has never changed.

499
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,200
In that case,

500
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,200
why did you kill my ally?

501
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:40,280
Who do you refer to? Deng Yi

502
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,680
or Zhong Changrong?

503
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,640
Or my brother Yanlai?

504
00:26:48,700 --> 00:26:49,860
Deng Yi and I fell out

505
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:52,280
because of the loss of Wangcheng.

506
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:54,520
Or even earlier.

507
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,080
Because Deng Yi

508
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:57,440
insisted on appointing Liang Qiang.

509
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,920
But now it seems

510
00:27:00,740 --> 00:27:02,300
that Liang Qiang was your mole.

511
00:27:02,780 --> 00:27:03,920
So, Deng Yi

512
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:04,920
was within your plan.

513
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:06,240
That's right.

514
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:08,280
Liang Qiang has always

515
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:09,160
served me.

516
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,640
At Xinggu Pass,

517
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,160
if he had killed Zhong Changrong

518
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:14,560
and replaced him,

519
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:16,040
it would have saved me

520
00:27:16,040 --> 00:27:17,240
a lot of trouble.

521
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,400
Sadly, Yanlai interfered.

522
00:27:20,520 --> 00:27:22,000
My foolproof plan

523
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,600
ended in ruin.

524
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:26,640
So,

525
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:30,000
he had to die.

526
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:33,240
Then you sent your men

527
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:34,880
to kill him and the enemy king?

528
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,400
Xiao Xun was

529
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,240
a perfect scapegoat.

530
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:41,000
Why wouldn't I?

531
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:43,600
Xiao Xun killed the enemy king

532
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:44,720
and my brother Yanlai.

533
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:46,080
There was solid evidence.

534
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,840
That you massacred Xiaonan

535
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,000
to avenge Yanlai

536
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:52,080
is also known to all.

537
00:27:52,560 --> 00:27:54,080
Now, even if you expose

538
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:54,840
the truth,

539
00:27:56,340 --> 00:27:57,880
who would believe you?

540
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:01,340
I know.

541
00:28:02,740 --> 00:28:03,880
Your Highness and Deng Yi

542
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,150
only differed in politics,

543
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:07,560
but you had to kill him yourself.

544
00:28:08,340 --> 00:28:09,180
Deep in your heart,

545
00:28:09,540 --> 00:28:11,180
you felt a little bit sad.

546
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,200
But the two of you

547
00:28:13,560 --> 00:28:15,440
couldn't coexist in the court.

548
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:17,440
So for your own good,

549
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:20,600
Deng Yi had to die.

550
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:22,760
Even so,

551
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:26,360
you shouldn't have interfered.

552
00:28:30,320 --> 00:28:31,640
I was helping you.

553
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:33,680
No need!

554
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:35,360
Xie Yanfang,

555
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:36,920
I'm not your plaything.

556
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,000
I'm different from those

557
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:39,520
you have tamed.

558
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,140
I won't become a puppet

559
00:28:41,140 --> 00:28:42,420
under your control.

560
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,640
Don't think you've won.

561
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:48,000
Because this game

562
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,560
isn't over yet.

563
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:53,140
Unless I'm dead,

564
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,160
you can never command

565
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,640
the frontier troops.

566
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,800
You've already lost, Your Highness.

567
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:05,600
A ruler must not have weak spots.

568
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:07,520
You show mercy

569
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,280
to so many trivial people and things.

570
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:11,840
You're bound to lose.

571
00:29:21,120 --> 00:29:21,680
Xie Yanfang,

572
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:23,080
what exactly do you want

573
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:24,360
from this trap of yours?

574
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:27,120
The frontier troops.

575
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:28,160
No way.

576
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:48,320
I'm not in a hurry.

577
00:29:49,360 --> 00:29:51,160
Take your time to think it over.

578
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:52,600
But if you

579
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:53,880
insist on refusing,

580
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:56,320
tomorrow, the whole world will know:

581
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,640
"The Grand Princess was assassinated during the hunt

582
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,640
and before death,

583
00:30:01,360 --> 00:30:03,520
Her Highness entrusted the Xie Clan with the military power."

584
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,400
Xie Yanfang,

585
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:09,240
you'll regret this.

586
00:30:10,360 --> 00:30:11,040
Regret?

587
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:16,720
I won't regret anything.

588
00:30:18,040 --> 00:30:19,360
Nor will you.

589
00:30:21,060 --> 00:30:21,700
Du Qi.

590
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:22,520
Here.

591
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:25,180
Send Her Highness back to her tent.

592
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,920
She must be tired.

593
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:47,920
Yu,

594
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,200
this is venison from today's hunt.

595
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,160
Eat while it's hot.

596
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,200
Are you going to kill Zhao?

597
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:02,040
What makes you say that?

598
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:03,920
I'm young,

599
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:05,640
but I'm not stupid.

600
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,720
Zhao is confined.

601
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,760
There are unusual troop moves.

602
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,680
Do you really think

603
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,720
I know nothing?

604
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:17,600
Your Majesty,

605
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:21,920
I just want to show Her Highness

606
00:31:22,760 --> 00:31:23,640
that some methods

607
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,280
just won't work.

608
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,960
If you can persuade Her Highness

609
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,960
to give me the Token,

610
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:31,000
I promise you.

611
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:33,560
She will be safe.

612
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,280
She's my sister!

613
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,280
The Grand Princess of State!

614
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:39,240
You...

615
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:40,120
You...

616
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:42,840
Are you forcing me to make my choice?

617
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:44,880
You're wrong.

618
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:50,040
It's Her Highness who will make her own choice.

619
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:51,960
To keep the military power

620
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,760
or to keep alive.

621
00:32:05,560 --> 00:32:07,400
I await your decision, Your Majesty.

622
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:34,200
Zhao,

623
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:35,720
I brought you some pastries.

624
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:36,960
Yu?

625
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:38,640
Why are you here?

626
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:40,000
It's cold at night.

627
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:41,320
You should have worn more.

628
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:42,440
Zhao,

629
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:43,960
are you hurt?

630
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:45,480
I'm fine.

631
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:46,600
Don't worry.

632
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,600
I don't want you to be confined.

633
00:32:50,560 --> 00:32:51,520
Let's give the Token

634
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,360
to Uncle Yanfang.

635
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:57,480
Yu,

636
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,520
do you know the meaning

637
00:32:59,840 --> 00:33:00,720
of the Frontier Troops Token?

638
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:04,000
Xie Yanfang represents the Xie Family.

639
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:06,960
If he seizes the military power

640
00:33:07,340 --> 00:33:08,540
and allows his clan to dominate,

641
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,400
it will be a total disaster.

642
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:12,360
I just want you to live.

643
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:13,880
He promised me.

644
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,480
As long as you meet his conditions...

645
00:33:17,360 --> 00:33:18,040
Don't worry.

646
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,440
We'll both be all right.

647
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:22,560
Someone will come to save us.

648
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:25,400
Who are you waiting for, Your Highness?

649
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:04,040
You guessed right.

650
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:06,880
The Longwei Army

651
00:34:07,280 --> 00:34:08,640
is invincible.

652
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,180
They live incognito

653
00:34:10,180 --> 00:34:11,320
and kill without a trace.

654
00:34:12,140 --> 00:34:12,920
Sadly,

655
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,880
since you became the Grand Princess

656
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:17,320
and the Longwei Army turned up,

657
00:34:18,120 --> 00:34:19,840
I have been investigating them.

658
00:34:21,660 --> 00:34:23,420
It took me a lot of time.

659
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,400
But now,

660
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:32,120
I know who they are.

661
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:35,360
So, I cut off their heads

662
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,760
one after another

663
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:39,080
and took off the yellow ribbons

664
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:41,080
as proof of their identities.

665
00:34:48,780 --> 00:34:50,580
You recognize this, don't you?

666
00:35:01,160 --> 00:35:02,520
You monster!

667
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:05,560
Zhao!

668
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:05,920
You...

669
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:07,540
You will pay for this!

670
00:35:08,420 --> 00:35:09,260
Me?

671
00:35:10,380 --> 00:35:12,260
They all died because of you.

672
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,480
Not just them.

673
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:17,020
If you really disobey,

674
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:19,880
I'll also massacre Cangmu Stronghold

675
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:22,200
and bring you the heads

676
00:35:22,200 --> 00:35:23,320
of Xiaoman and her men.

677
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:25,680
What do you say?

678
00:35:28,900 --> 00:35:29,580
Your Highness,

679
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:31,380
Just admit your defeat.

680
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:33,660
Why don't you just kill me?

681
00:35:34,560 --> 00:35:35,560
Then you will have

682
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:36,980
the court

683
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:38,860
and the frontier troops!

684
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:55,860
If you die,

685
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,940
Yu will be very sad.

686
00:36:13,980 --> 00:36:14,780
Anyway,

687
00:36:16,520 --> 00:36:18,720
I'm waiting for you

688
00:36:19,780 --> 00:36:21,420
to surrender of your own will.

689
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:06,020
The frontier troops and Mr. Zhong

690
00:37:08,680 --> 00:37:10,160
only obey this token.

691
00:37:57,020 --> 00:37:58,460
This dagger is coated with Golden Finch Venom.

692
00:37:58,980 --> 00:38:00,660
Xie Yanfang, you'll die!

693
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:11,740
Well, you've grown.

694
00:38:13,220 --> 00:38:14,680
You've even learned to use poison.

695
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:17,600
There's no antidote for this poison.

696
00:38:18,220 --> 00:38:19,000
Xie Yanfang,

697
00:38:19,460 --> 00:38:20,820
you're going to die!

698
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:23,260
You would sacrifice your own life

699
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:24,620
just to kill me?

700
00:38:24,620 --> 00:38:25,140
Yes!

701
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:28,020
I want you dead!

702
00:38:36,780 --> 00:38:37,620
Zhao, run!

703
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:39,560
Your Majesty.

704
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:40,280
I order you

705
00:38:40,560 --> 00:38:41,480
to drop your weapons!

706
00:38:56,900 --> 00:38:59,020
This breaks my heart.

707
00:39:04,040 --> 00:39:05,080
Seize her.

708
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:08,480
Dead or alive.

709
00:39:09,060 --> 00:39:10,020
- Yes! - Yes!

710
00:39:11,460 --> 00:39:12,100
Your Majesty.

711
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:53,000
Stop!

712
00:39:53,160 --> 00:39:53,760
Don't run!

713
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:55,880
Stop!

714
00:39:56,180 --> 00:39:56,900
Catch her!

715
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:57,580
Stop!

716
00:39:58,920 --> 00:39:59,520
Hurry!

717
00:40:00,040 --> 00:40:00,720
Stop running!

718
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:01,960
Stop!

719
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:33,120
♪Broken walls and withered branches, trapped in the mire♪

720
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,880
♪Yet still striving to reach for the sky♪

721
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:39,960
♪My pride is torn down and my body is sacrificed♪

722
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:44,320
♪The spark smolders in the crack♪

723
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,360
♪And roars in the blaze♪

724
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:49,680
♪Burning the cold night until daybreak♪

725
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:52,080
♪Fate imprisons me♪

726
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:57,040
♪But I won't beg the abyss for mercy♪

727
00:40:57,040 --> 00:41:01,240
♪Even if hope is faint, I remain proud♪

728
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:05,520
♪A mayfly will cross the ocean, however long it takes♪

729
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:10,960
♪However it ends up, I'll go my own way♪

730
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,920
♪With no fear of the distance♪

731
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:16,640
♪Born from decay, fireflies still burn♪

732
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:21,080
♪With sword in hand, I'll pierce the dawn♪

733
00:41:21,080 --> 00:41:26,440
♪Let these scars all over me become♪

734
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:30,040
♪My new pride♪

735
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:47,720
♪Peril is everywhere in the palace♪

736
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:50,240
♪Yet I smile to nobody but you♪

737
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:52,600
♪Amidst the chaos♪

738
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:56,880
♪I'll always be with you♪

739
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:00,440
♪The spark smolders in the crack♪

740
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:02,480
♪And roars in the blaze♪

741
00:42:02,560 --> 00:42:05,800
♪Burning the cold night until daybreak♪

742
00:42:05,960 --> 00:42:08,200
♪Fate imprisons me♪

743
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:13,160
♪But I won't beg the abyss for mercy♪

744
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:17,360
♪Even if hope is faint, I remain proud♪

745
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:21,640
♪A mayfly will cross the ocean, however long it takes♪

746
00:42:21,640 --> 00:42:27,080
♪However it ends up, I'll go my own way♪

747
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:29,040
♪With no fear of the distance♪

748
00:42:29,040 --> 00:42:32,760
♪Born from decay, fireflies still burn♪

749
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:37,200
♪With sword in hand, I'll pierce the dawn♪

750
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:42,560
♪Let these scars all over me become♪

751
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:46,160
♪My new pride♪
